This is a mirror of http://www.vim.org/scripts/script.php?script_id=3692

quickhl.vim is minimal utility for

* quickly highlight `<cword>`
* quickly highlight visually selected text.

quickhl.vim not provide any keymap by default.  see help.

### ScreenCast
http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=W_XJlTbuoyI

### Github
https://github.com/t9md/vim-quickhl

